# API Controller Rules

## Endpoint Patterns
- `GET /resource` -- List (paginated)
- `GET /resource/:id` -- Get single
- `POST /resource` -- Create
- `PATCH /resource/:id` -- Partial update
- `DELETE /resource/:id` -- Delete

## Pagination
- Use query params: `?page=1&limit=20`
- Return: `{ data: T[], total: number, page: number, limit: number }`

## Authentication
- All endpoints require `@UseGuards(JwtAuthGuard)` unless decorated with `@Public()`
- Company-scoped endpoints verify membership via `CompanyMemberGuard`
- Admin-only endpoints use `@Roles('admin', 'owner')` decorator

## Swagger
- Every controller uses `@ApiTags('domain-name')`
- Every endpoint has `@ApiOperation({ summary: '...' })`
- Response types documented with `@ApiResponse()`

## Request Validation
- All body DTOs validated via `ValidationPipe` (global)
- Path params validated with `ParseUUIDPipe`
- Query params use dedicated Query DTO classes
